title: 'Selling Sunset' Season 5 Preview Show
description:
Juliet Litman is joined by 'Tea Time' host Liz Kelly to prepare us for the upcoming season of Netflix’s 'Selling Sunset.' They recap everything that went down last season and discuss which elements of this “reality” show are actually real.
Hosts: Juliet Litman and Liz Kelly
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
